77
00:06:05,950 --> 00:06:06,980
Won what? Hurry up!

78
00:06:07,070 --> 00:06:07,490
Something happened!

79
00:06:07,630 --> 00:06:08,460
Jiaqi got into a fight!

80
00:06:08,510 --> 00:06:08,900
Who?

81
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:09,780
Jiaqi!

82
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:10,580
Where?

83
00:06:10,950 --> 00:06:11,540
Come with me!

84
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:12,700
Hurry!

85
00:06:13,950 --> 00:06:14,700
Who's that bad?

86
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,250
Where is he?

87
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,100
Are you still with him?

88
00:06:18,390 --> 00:06:18,980
Where is he?

89
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:20,610
At school?

90
00:06:21,070 --> 00:06:21,580
School!

91
00:06:21,750 --> 00:06:22,780
- Go! - Get him!

92
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,540
Get him!

93
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:27,490
Jiaqi!

94
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,050
Jiaqi!

95
00:06:28,270 --> 00:06:28,580
Jiaqi!

96
00:06:29,510 --> 00:06:30,020
You're here.

97
00:06:30,950 --> 00:06:31,370
What happened?

98
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,050
Who hit you?

99
00:06:32,170 --> 00:06:33,070
How'd you get hurt this bad?

100
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:33,670
Who did it?

101
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:34,290
You okay?

102
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,050
I'm fine.

103
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,250
What are you guys doing?

104
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:36,980
What do you mean fine?

105
00:06:36,980 --> 00:06:37,700
Look at you!

106
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:38,270
Where is he?

107
00:06:38,310 --> 00:06:39,160
Where's the guy who hit you?

108
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:40,410
Zhang, where is he?

109
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:41,930
I didn't see what happened either.

110
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,540
I was just passing by the school,

111
00:06:43,870 --> 00:06:45,220
and I saw Jiaqi there.

112
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,460
Seeing him like that,

113
00:06:46,830 --> 00:06:47,540
I couldn't just leave.

114
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,980
So I called Chi right away.

115
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,780
Jiaqi, what is going on?

116
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,050
Some guy

117
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:54,900
bumped into me.

118
00:06:54,950 --> 00:06:55,660
No manners at all.

119
00:06:55,870 --> 00:06:56,700
So we started fighting.

120
00:06:57,070 --> 00:06:58,220
It's handled. I'm fine.

121
00:06:58,630 --> 00:06:59,410
By the school, right?

122
00:06:59,950 --> 00:07:00,370
Yeah.

123
00:07:00,500 --> 00:07:01,380
Jialu, what are you doing?

124
00:07:01,380 --> 00:07:02,580
Jialu!

125
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,410
What happened exactly?

126
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:06,140
This isn't like you.

127
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:06,900
Jiaqi,

128
00:07:07,390 --> 00:07:08,140
tell me the truth.

129
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,540
This was not just a bump.

130
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:10,410
What happened?

131
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,220
Circle up!

132
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:15,810
It's a critical time for Jiaqi.

133
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:16,660
He can't end up at the station.

134
00:07:16,830 --> 00:07:17,140
Okay.

135
00:07:17,310 --> 00:07:18,100
Get moving!

136
00:07:21,390 --> 00:07:21,930
Patrolling?

137
00:07:23,630 --> 00:07:24,660
It's late at night.

138
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,370
What are you doing

139
00:07:25,390 --> 00:07:26,370
