140
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:29,020
We're Pure Friendship.

141
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,580
The big match is coming up.

142
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:31,850
We're out here training.

143
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,100
Training on the street?

144
00:07:34,390 --> 00:07:35,810
In the daytime we're all at work,

145
00:07:35,870 --> 00:07:36,660
no time, right?

146
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,660
Only at night

147
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:38,540
can we meet up

148
00:07:38,630 --> 00:07:39,290
and train.

149
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,900
Hurry! Let's move!

150
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:41,850
- Yeah, no time! - No time!

151
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,610
It's this late and you still have to patrol.

152
00:07:44,690 --> 00:07:45,520
Have some water.

153
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,320
Who's got water?

154
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:46,700
No, thanks.

155
00:07:46,700 --> 00:07:47,460
No need.

156
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:48,610
Keep training.

157
00:07:50,030 --> 00:07:50,460
See you!

158
00:07:50,630 --> 00:07:51,540
- Thanks for your work! - Thanks for your work!

159
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,170
Sorry about that!

160
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:54,810
They're really dedicated.

161
00:07:54,810 --> 00:07:55,850
Keep going...

162
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,900
Why's there a lady on the men's team?

163
00:08:00,070 --> 00:08:01,020
I'm their coach!

164
00:08:01,870 --> 00:08:02,370
She's the coach!

165
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:03,850
Coach,

166
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:05,140
why can't I pick up speed

167
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:06,410
on my 500 meters?

168
00:08:06,630 --> 00:08:07,580
You just don't train enough.

169
00:08:07,760 --> 00:08:08,370
Really?

170
00:08:08,370 --> 00:08:09,050
You need to train harder.

171
00:08:09,310 --> 00:08:09,810
Tonight,

172
00:08:09,870 --> 00:08:11,050
let's do a 5K together.

173
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:12,810
- Okay! - Okay!

174
00:08:13,190 --> 00:08:13,610
Let's train!

175
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:16,620
One-two-three-four! Two-two-three-four!

176
00:08:17,070 --> 00:08:18,580
Three-two-three-four!

177
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:19,460
Hey!

178
00:08:19,460 --> 00:08:20,330
Hey, Jialu!

179
00:08:20,330 --> 00:08:21,080
- Jialu! - Don't do anything stupid!

180
00:08:21,390 --> 00:08:22,850
- Jialu! - Hold him back!

181
00:08:22,870 --> 00:08:23,370
Don't be rash!

182
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:24,050
Don't do it!

183
00:08:24,070 --> 00:08:24,780
[Qingxi Road Primary School]
Slow down!

184
00:08:24,950 --> 00:08:25,610
Stop!

185
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:26,340
Stop!

186
00:08:27,190 --> 00:08:27,780
You're not going!

187
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:29,850
Get back here!

188
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,290
Hey...

189
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,370
Where are you?

190
00:08:31,390 --> 00:08:31,970
Don't do anything stupid!

191
00:08:31,970 --> 00:08:32,460
Come out!

192
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:34,110
Who hit my brother?

193
00:08:34,110 --> 00:08:34,780
Stop yelling!

194
00:08:34,870 --> 00:08:35,820
Come back with me!

195
00:08:36,420 --> 00:08:36,770
Easy!

196
00:08:36,770 --> 00:08:37,850
Calm down!

197
00:08:40,870 --> 00:08:41,610
Police!

198
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:46,130
It's the middle of the night.

199
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,130
What are you yelling for?

200
00:08:48,550 --> 00:08:49,420
Pure Friendship?

201
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:50,770
You again?

202
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:52,380
You split into two groups

203
00:08:52,380 --> 00:08:53,580
for night running now?

204
00:08:53,910 --> 00:08:54,530
Your mates just made a scene over there,

205
00:08:54,550 --> 00:08:55,420
and now you're causing trouble here too?

206
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,610
We split into two groups

207
00:08:56,670 --> 00:08:57,610
and worked out a bit.

208
00:08:57,790 --> 00:08:58,700
We're leaving now!

209
00:08:59,120 --> 00:08:59,580
Alright.

210
00:08:59,630 --> 00:09:00,530
Get back home!

211
00:09:00,870 --> 00:09:01,370
No more trouble.

212
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:04,130
Go.

213
00:09:06,060 --> 00:09:09,220
