221
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:22,760
Usually, if there's a commotion on the street,

222
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:23,650
you'd take a detour.

223
00:09:23,870 --> 00:09:24,850
Now one little bump,

224
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:25,940
and you get into a fight,

225
00:09:26,150 --> 00:09:27,130
and end up like this?

226
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:29,130
