227
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,610
You didn't see that punk...

228
00:09:35,030 --> 00:09:36,340
Let's just drop it.

229
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:37,180
No.

230
00:09:37,870 --> 00:09:38,850
We have to find him.

231
00:09:40,790 --> 00:09:41,460
What do you want to do?

232
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,340
Fight him again?

233
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:44,850
Kill him?

234
00:09:45,150 --> 00:09:46,130
Yao Dongshan, what's your problem?

235
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,370
You were always like,

236
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:49,650
"Uncle's here, don't worry."

237
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:50,940
And now you're chickening out?

238
00:09:51,150 --> 00:09:52,130
When did I chicken out?

239
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,650
You remember that?

240
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,300
