244
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:08,850
You should worry about

245
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,610
how to explain this to your family.

246
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:15,370
These days,

247
00:10:16,390 --> 00:10:17,610
don't go to visit your mom.

248
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,220
Like hiding is going to help.

249
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,370
So what do we do?

250
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:22,420
Just say he's busy at work,

251
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,610
and he'll drop by after a while.

252
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:25,130
Can you guarantee

253
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,650
Mom won't go looking for him?

254
00:10:27,630 --> 00:10:28,850
