257
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,300
My mom's not stupid.

258
00:10:33,790 --> 00:10:35,180
You can't fall and end up like this!

259
00:10:35,550 --> 00:10:36,300
Besides,

260
00:10:36,390 --> 00:10:37,770
