261
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:39,530
We're still discussing it!

262
00:10:39,790 --> 00:10:40,460
What's your idea?

263
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:45,610
How about this?

264
00:10:46,030 --> 00:10:47,220
We'll say it was from playing soccer.

265
00:10:47,670 --> 00:10:48,460
While playing,

266
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:49,420
he got into a shouting match.

267
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:50,650
It kept escalating,

268
00:10:50,870 --> 00:10:52,060
and it turned into a fight.

269
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,530
That works!

270
00:10:53,670 --> 00:10:54,220
If you get heated,

271
00:10:54,390 --> 00:10:55,370
isn't fighting pretty normal?

272
00:10:55,550 --> 00:10:56,060
That won't work!

273
00:10:56,230 --> 00:10:57,340
Ask around

274
00:10:57,340 --> 00:10:58,060
within ten miles,

275
00:10:58,270 --> 00:10:59,150
who'd dare

276
00:10:59,150 --> 00:11:00,220
mess with Pure Friendship?

277
00:11:00,870 --> 00:11:01,850
You're joking, really.

278
00:11:03,250 --> 00:11:03,940
Besides,

279
00:11:04,020 --> 00:11:05,180
with his face scratched up like this,

280
00:11:05,390 --> 00:11:06,850
Mom's going to ask who did it.

281
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,130
His wife's going to ask too.

282
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:08,890
So who?

283
00:11:09,630 --> 00:11:10,460
Who's taking the blame?

284
00:11:28,540 --> 00:11:30,960
[Galaxy Tavern]

285
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:32,300
You should worry about

286
00:11:32,790 --> 00:11:34,060
how to explain this to your family.

287
